text: Wenatchee is a city in Washington State, the United States of America. The city has a population of about 35,000. It is served by Pangborn Memorial Airport. == Other websites == *The City of Wenatchee, Washington , city government website. *Port of Chelan County, county port district. *Wenatchee Valley Convention & Visitors Bureau, area convention and visitors center. *Wenatchee Valley Chamber of Commerce, area chamber of commerce. *Wenatchee Downtown Association, downtown association. * Category:Cities in Washington (state) Category:County seats in Washington (state)
